body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting Car Dealership Support. My name is Elijah Nelson. May I have your name please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello, my name is Dorothy Bailey.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Dorothy. How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling surprised because I have not received the shipping confirmation for my recent car purchase.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand your concern. To assist you further, could you please provide me with your order number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, the order number is seven three four eight two.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Dorothy. Additionally, to verify your account, may I have the last four digits of your phone number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Yes, the last four digits are five six seven eight.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing the details, Dorothy. I will look into this matter for you. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that was all. Thank you.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for reaching out, Dorothy. Your issue will be addressed promptly. Have a great day!
